quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  38,27,"Ne shikhwaloonga likulu nende eshialo, nende ebili hakari wabio eshikhaya tawe. Ako ni amaparo ka balia abakhaya. Kho eshinyasio eshilulu shiomulilo shilinyoola balia Abakhaya."
  38,28,"Nohomba khukhole balia basubila babe shinga balia bakholanga amabii khushialo, nohomba khukhole abaria Nyasaye shinga abetsimbii?"
  38,29,"Eshitabu shino shakhwakhwishilia ewe ni sha tsikhabi tsinyinji kho banyoole okhupaara mutsinyaali tsiashio, ne abandu ba amachesi banyoole okhuwulila."
  38,30,"Ne khwahelesia Dawudi Suleiman yali Omusumba omulayi muno, toto ye yali omunji wokhukalushila Nyasaye."
  38,31,"Olwa yalolwesibwa mubise bya ingolobe (lasiri) tsinyumbu tsia tsimbiro mana khandi tsindai po."
  38,32,"Mana naboola mbu: “Toto esie ndachama ebindu ebilayi okhushila okhwitsulila Nyasaye wanje Omulesi", okhula (tsifarasi etso) nitsikhamukha mushirima (Suleiman niyenya mbu atsilole khandi)."
  38,33,""Tsikalusie khwisie.” Mana nachaka okhutsitilakhwo mwikosi nende khubilenje."
  38,34,"Ne toto khwatema Suleiman, nenikhura omubili khushisaala shishie, mana nakalukha okhusaba eshileshelo."
  38,35,"Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, ndeshela, ne mbelesia obwaami bwomundu wundi alalinyoola inyuma wanje tawe. Toto ewe newe Omuwani watoto.”"
  38,36,"Mana nikhukhola omuyeka okhumurumushila, kwachendanga khubulomesi bubwe hosi hosi ayenya okhuula."
  38,37,"Mana nikhukhola amashetani okhumurumushila, koosi kombakhanga nende keyibilanga mumatsi."
  38,38,"Nende akaandi kaboyungwa khuminyororo."
  38,39,"Shino ni eshihanwa shiefu. Kho mana rusia nohomba shitiile, shibula eshichelo."
  38,40,"Ne toto ye ewefu ali nende eshisaala shia hambi muno nefwe, nende habundu halayi muno wokhukalukha."
  38,41,"Ne yitsulila Omusumba wefu Ayub, olwa yalanga Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi mbu: “Toto esie Shetani yanderere obusinyifu nende obusandi.”"
  38,42,"Nyasaye namuboolela mbu: “Sieba hasi eshilenje shishio (isebele nirundukha hasi awo). Kano namatsi amanyifu kokhwisinga nende kokhunywa.”"